Use arrays when you need order

When are they slow?

Big O of arrays
    insertion: depends...
    removal: depends...
    searching: O(n)
    Access: O(1)

.push: O(1)
.pop: O(1)
.unshift: O(n)
.shift: O(n)
.concat: O(n)
.slice: O(n)
.splice: O(n)
.sort(n * log n) ...oh dip
forEach/map/filter/reduce/etc: O(n)
